						               													<description>Nichtlustig: Noch mehr Labor Chaos is a card game set in the world of the Nichtlustig comics of Joscha Sauer. 80 unique and uniquely illustrated cards generate all sorts of effects that are often hilarious and bring much laughter to the table. Each player is dealt a hand of 7 cards and has to get rid of them as quickly as possible, but other players will force them to draw new cards throughout the game.&amp;#10;The great variety of effects on the cards generate endless combinations and surprises. Players try to shake this explosive cocktail without being the one duped. This successor of Labor Chaos can effortlessly be mixed with it, so that many more surprises can be expected. These games are just as well played by 8 year old kids as by their 88 year old grandparents. You can also play it with strangers on a train and there is even a card that allows you to give it to the conductor so that he can join the game for a little while!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Integrates with:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    NichtLustig: Labor Chaos&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
